text.tspan: Weekly case growth rate vs. daily case rate, Jun 30, 2021
Shown on the x-axis is the average case rate over the last 7 days.
Shown on the y-axis is the week over week increase in new confirmed cases.
The color indicates the share of COVID-19 tests that are positive.
